Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:06.63,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}洗完脸 刷好牙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.47,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}来吧One！（One！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:12.02,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Two！（Two！）Three！冲出门吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.18,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}穿上漂亮衣服（哦？）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:16.44,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}吃光点心（啊？）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:20.86,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}大家友好地牵起手来和着歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:25.28,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Dowa Dowa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:31.49,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}来 跳舞吧！开！始！咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:33.95,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}一直都 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:36.08,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}永远 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:40.63,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}身体按耐不住喜悦 露出欢欣笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:42.75,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}更加 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:45.34,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}大家 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:49.64,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}传达到吧 不论天涯海角（再来一遍！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:52.10,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}一直都 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.31,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}永远 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:58.69,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}心中难耐着激动 大家欢喜雀跃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.90,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}更加 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:03.36,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}大家 Happy Happy Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:08.53,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}今天明天知道永远 大家都是好朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:10.53,edjp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:02.30,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}朝飛び起きて　窓を開けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:06.63,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}顔を洗って　ハミガキをして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.47,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}さあワン！（ワン！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:12.02,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}ツー！（ツー！）スリー！で飛び　出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.18,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}お洒落な服を着て　（お？）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:16.44,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}お菓子を平らげて　（え？）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:20.86,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}仲良く手をつないでみんなで声合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:25.28,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}デュワデュワ　デュワデュワ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:31.49,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}さあ踊ろう！　い！く！よー！
